            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EWhat%20a%20powerful%20witness%20it%20is%20to%20walk%20in%20the%20light!%20Paul%20actually%20states%20that%20a%20clean%2C%20pure%20walk%20with%20the%20Lord%20is%20what%20helps%20us%20to%20commend%20ourselves%20to%20others.%20The%20process%20is%20actually%20very%20simple.%20The%20Holy%20Spirit%20shines%20the%20light%20of%20Christ%20upon%20our%20lives%2C%20changing%20us%20%22from%20glory%20to%20glory%22%20(2%20Corinthians%203%3A18%20KJV).%20That%20unveiled%20glory%20is%20then%20reflected%20from%20our%20faces%20to%20a%20darkened%2C%20oppressed%20world%20whose%20eyes%20have%20been%20blinded%20by%20the%20%22god%20of%20this%20evil%20world%22%20(4%3A4).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%22For%20God%2C%20who%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98Let%20there%20be%20light%20in%20the%20darkness%2C'%20has%20made%20us%20understand%20that%20this%20light%20is%20the%20brightness%20of%20the%20glory%20of%20God%20that%20is%20seen%20in%20the%20face%20of%20Jesus%20Christ%22%20(4%3A6).%20From%20within%20these%20%22perishable%20containers%22%20(v.%207)%20shines%20out%20the%20very%20glory%20of%20the%20Creator%20God%20who%20spoke%20a%20billion%20suns%20into%20existence%20in%20one%20moment!%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20are%20%22full%20of%20light%20from%20the%20Lord%22%20(Ephesians%205%3A8)%2C%20and%20as%20we%20walk%20in%20the%20purity%20of%20Jesus'%20face%2C%20a%20lost%20world%20will%20behold%20Him.%20We%20walk%20through%20pressure%2C%20perplexity%2C%20and%20persecution%20with%20victory%2C%20so%20that%20the%20%22life%20of%20Jesus%20may%20also%20be%20seen%20in%20our%20bodies%22%20(2%20Corinthians%204%3A10).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOur%20greatest%20witness%3F%20Our%20radiant%20shine!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
